    Verse: 9
Tags:
  - Saints
---
The wonderful thing about saints is that they were human. They
lost their tempers, got hungry, scolded God, were egotistical or testy or
impatient in their turns, made mistakes and regretted them. Still they went
on doggedly blundering toward heaven.
